# 13. Why This Architecture Works

It mimics a **real ML team**:

| Agent              | Real Role               |
| ------------------ | ----------------------- |
| Notebook Reader    | Data ingestion engineer |
| Code Understanding | ML analyst              |
| Pipeline Planner   | ML architect            |
| Code Refactor      | ML engineer             |
| Feature Agent      | Data scientist          |
| Training Agent     | ML engineer             |
| Evaluation Agent   | Model validator         |
| Packaging Agent    | MLOps engineer          |

So your system becomes a **virtual ML team**.

